  "keyFeatures": [
    "Chat with documents using RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation)",
    "Support for 30+ LLM providers (OpenAI, Anthropic, Ollama, Gemini, etc.)",
    "Built-in AI agents with web browsing, file creation, and SQL capabilities",
    "No-code agent flow builder for automated multi-step workflows",
    "MCP (Model Context Protocol) server compatibility",
    "Multi-user support with role-based access control (Docker only)",
    "11+ vector database integrations (Chroma, Pinecone, Qdrant, Weaviate, etc.)",
    "Embeddable chat widget for websites",
    "Dynamic Model Router for automatic provider/model selection",
    "Automatic and user-managed memory injection",
    "Scheduled recurring tasks with full agent capabilities",
    "Intelligent skill reranking — reduces token usage by up to 80%",
    "OpenAI-compatible API for drop-in integration",
    "Desktop app for Mac, Windows, and Linux"
  ],
